Question: How would you invite your friends to a party if phones and the Internet did not exist?
Answer:
There are various of different ways to invite friends to a  party even through there is no phones or internet.
First, if you know their address, you can drive or walk to their home directly and inform them in person.
Besides, if you share some common friendsfriend who has more convenient access to them. You could ask them to pass the  message.